即場拘捕，將他放走。<br />\n<br />\n一批男人在近北角英皇道聚集，地上放有長竹，警員曾上前勸他們返回行人路，但他們未有理會，一直跟隨警員推進。<br />\n<br />\n去到炮台山，<span style=\"color: red;\">其中一人用摺椅襲擊其他人，一批警員到場。該批施襲的男人退到警員的後面，一會兒後，繼續與警員一起推進。</span><br />\n<br />\n去炮台山，再追打幾名黑衣人入港鐵站。回到地面，用摺椅擊打另一人的頭部。大批防暴警員到場制止，<span style=\"color: red;\">將用摺椅施襲的白衣男人帶到一邊，截查一段時間後將他放走</span>，有途人不滿。<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，多名男子推另一名男士，警員到場將懷疑推人的男子帶上警車，警員亦在現場帶走多名相信是示威者。<br />\n<br />\n一段時間後，早前用摺椅施襲的一批人士繼續在北角街頭出現。一名警員曾上前想阻止他們全部離開，但不成功。<br />\n<br />\n北角晚上多次出現打鬥，防暴警察在場戒備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=362858&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362858%26refer%3D&d=02TnLe2cOfQrY9jdqtoXeU9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=bd0f09d5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D362858%26refer%3D&h=3ed08434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=362858&amp;refer=</a>"},{"pid":"3ab4b48c4faff10d1333ec55af36d6d8cbb676f9","tid":1571984,"uid":275175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:07:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">施行酷刑施行酷刑施行酷刑施行酷刑施行酷刑</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"51e1295d1ada20de75e8cc70cf5c4f6d9b556bd2","tid":1571984,"uid":143682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T15:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif